lead_paragraph: Newly released court documents include excerpts from emails showing that Wisconsin Gov. Scott Walker's recall election campaign team told him to instruct donors to give to a key conservative group that would run ads for Walker and distribute money to other conservative groups backing him.

headline.main: Emails Show Walker Recall Election Campaign Push
headline.print_headline: Emails Show Walker Recall Election Campaign Push
